title: GoPro: Dog Plays Ball With Brazilian Footballer Gabigol
description:
On the sandy shores of Ipanema Beach, Scotch the Border Collie goes head-to-head with Brazilian soccer star Gabriel "Gabigol" Barbosa, in a friendly match of Futevolei.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music Courtesy of ExtremeMusic
